reviews.text: Laksa was only Ok, as far as Laksa goes. But the steak lunch specials with rice and sauce was very nice and made it worth the visit.
Recommended curry beef rice.

Not the King it claims to be
Better laksa next door at Affinity
the shop was small and not well decorated. The Laksa soup was not rich enough, so it was bit disappointing.
The foods are ok enough for the cost.
